The paper discusses the theoretical foundations of deep learning and its possible connection to the renormalization group (RG) framework. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.ST (Statistics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
